Text: Initializing automated ley lines... Resuming magic combat!
Aether levels critical... Reinitializing emergency shutdown...
Energy output critical... Resuming combat on auxiliary power...
Auxiliary power critical... Combat protocols unsustainable...
Altering combat protocol... Melee unit assemble!
Altering combat protocol... Ranged unit assemble!
I never asked for this, kupo...

Clear a path!
Cut through them!

The legatus cannot be far,
but we must be swift.

Stop them!
No one gets through!

We are VIth Legion!
Show them what that means!
The emperor will not be denied!

Lord Forgall!
Your will is my command!

Wait, you don't want me!
Surely the captain...

Please!
I don't want to die!
The people are counting on us. We must protect them at all costs!
Fear not, the Go Go Posing Rangers are here!
Leave the Bombard King to us!
Your demise is nigh, fiend! We'll reclaim these oceans, and see that you inflict no further harm!
Adventurers, take care of the minions!
Go! Go! Triple Majestic Slash Attack!
Go! Go! Raging Flame Reverse-blow Punch!
Well done, Rangers! Our job here is finished!
Careful, those're filled with cannon powder!
He's...\<pant>...too strong! \<pant> Rangers, we must retreat!
Stand firm, Rangers! Against our combined strength, he has no chance!
We have him right where we want him!

Shkoh! Shkoh! Sneaky-taken
jinglyshine, where are yooou?

Jinglyshine, jinglyshine,♪
What is yours will soon be mine...♪

Which way? Which way?
Braincase throbs with indecision...

No busydeals for greedy uplander!
Jinglyshine is for feeding little gobbies!

No jinglyshine is eyecatched...
How to buy cheese for gobbieflock...?

Shkohhh! Uplander having
lustyeyes for jinglyshine!?

If uplander come at gobbie,
uplander best bring whole flock!

Shkoh! Shkoh! More jinglyshine
for starving little gobbies!

Psheew... Mercy, mercy!
Backwalk to wife and little gobbies!
We said we'd...make a name for ourselves...
Wh-What is this place? Where are the others?
Oh, Dolorous. Even in death...I will always...
I must have that chocobo egg... It's the only way...
I am undying...? Was it the elixir?
You hear that, lads? The sea's callin' me home...
Where are my men...?  Clovissoix, Dhavha!

Hie thee onwards!
I need no assistance!

If more come,
I will handle them!

This must be it...
Their secrets will be mine!
To stop the ceremony, they come!
O Lady Garuda, to me grant strength!
For the eyes, go! For the eyes! Squaaak!
Fly from this sacred place, featherless ones will!
From on high, we rain down death!

The aether! Hngh!
It's not enough!
You won't get away this time!
Ugh... Let it not be in vain...
I can feel it! Just a little more!
One with the wind, we become...

Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Uplander moves, uplander gets cut with stabbysteel!

Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Uplander blindsteps right into sneakytrap!
Pshhh... Shkohhh... Uplanders are needing to die...nowtimes!

Pshhh... Shkohhh...
For make glorious nation of Illuminati, uplanders must die!
For glory of Quickthinx, gobbies must be strong!

I think they want
to plaaAaaaAaay...!
Welcome! We have a special treat for you...
A new toy for me? I do love toys.
Oh, this will be so much fun!
My lovelies...see that our friends have a good time.
This is the most fun we've had in yeeEeeEars!
'Fraid we can't let you pass, ribbit!
Intruders? They'll make a fine supper, ribbit!
You still live? Not for long...!

Just beyond lies all our mochi!
Please make haste, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>! What's left of our precious mochi is being devoured as we speak!
Be sure to avoid the cyclops's mallet, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>, lest you also are pounded into a fine paste!
Quickly, quickly now, else we'll have nothing to distribute to the citizens!
Fantastic! At this rate, we'll have more than enough mochi to feed the masses!
Oh, no! It seems we are too late...
Laniaitte... Francel... I wish you all...
Lord van Baelsar... Even in death...I serve...
No! I can't die... Not like this...
Dyin' a third time... Forgive me, Diamanda...
Shkoh! Uplander comes close, gets special surprise!
Uplanders think they are safe in farplace? Think again!
Shkoh! Uplanders will feel much pain!

We have them outnumbered!
Crush these fools!
Impossible! This was the latest design...

Activating surplus ceruleum propulsion. 
Engaging enemy.

Structural integrity compromised.
Initiating withdrawal protocol...
Let's see you squirm out of this!

\<hiss>
There is a decidedly
foul scent on the air!

We come for you,
Shadow Queen!

Close your eyes,
and never awaken!

Tendrils of shadow!
Hearken to my call!

I didn't sign up
for this...

How many times
must I hit you!?
Here is where the pounding takes place!
Please help us retrieve the mochi!
Watch the cyclops's swing and have care you aren't pounded into paste!
The fate of the mochi is in your hands!
That was a truly inspiring display! Why, even Taro has regained his cheer!

What say we try
something new!?
And now, for my next trick...

You bring this fate
upon yourself!

Be you one or many,
this battle is ours!
Look upon a samurai of Doma!
The Griffin has spoken! Kill them all!
You'll not spoil our moment of glory!
This is some kind of nightmare...

Any one of you run,
and I'll gut you myself!

And risk losin' me cut?
Not on yer life!
With you to the end, sir!

No man what wanted to
live would turn his back
on that there beast!
You were always my favorite, boss!

I'm fairly certain
this constitutes the end!

Look! Over there!
No really, look!
Why you craven sons of... Wait for me!!!
Tonight, we'll dine like kings, friend!
I can smell the rump roasting already...
An assault from the rear would provide us with the element of surprise...
And we mustn't forget to consider wind direction...
Victory! Let us flay the beast and haul the carcass back to camp!
All that blood... I think I've lost my appetite...
Over here, little one. I have some tasty leaves for you...
I don't know if this is going to work...
Thal's hoarfrosted balls! It's the mother!
Stand your ground, you whore-spawned shi─ Wait for me!!!
Ooh ooh! Ooh ooh! Ooh ooh!
From the heart of the mountain...
To the eye of the storm...

So do the waters flow
till lasting bridges form.
I'm a little frightened, but I can do this!
According to the aetherometer, this area should be teeming with shards...
Ah, that is quite enough for today!
I am ruined! There aren't enough shards here to fill a gil purse!
Very well, then. It is off to the next location.
On behalf of House Haillenarte, you have my thanks.
And do take care on your journey home. The Diadem yet brims with peril.
Ye kindly adventurers! House Haillenarte is seeking aid in the collection of crystal shards!
A thousand curses on that damnable whoreson!
I'll see you in the seventh hell...
Many thanks, adventurer. And please...do not tell my master of this...

Foulest of foul westlanders!
You've not heard last of us!
Seize them, before the Sekiseigumi come!

Where did that brat
come from!?
Send them to the Seventh Gate!
This Namazu's more heavy than he looks...
He's also slimier and─\<sniff> \<sniff>─could really do with a bath...

Keep those things
away from the camp!

We would have been at a
loss without you, adventurer.

The Qalyana will pay
for their thievery!
Let's see how strong you truly are!
It's time to unleash my true power!
Know the power of the coeurl!
I spy a chink in your armor!

You can run...er, fly, but you
cannot hide! We will have ourglory another day!

Hah hah! We'll need a
bigger cookfire this night!

Straight and true...
Straight and true...
I will be back! I swear it!
There is no shame in retreat!

H-How can you
be so strong?

It was everything...
I had hoped for...

Where are they
all coming from?

They've lured
us into a trap!

The hills are safe once again.
The Resistance thanks you.
We may just make it yet!

We march.
You, take the rear guard.

How's a man to eat if he's
without aught to harvest...?

Twelve be praised!
The fields are saved!

With any luck, I'll be
spared my aunt's whip!

The day belongs
to the Dotharl!
